sub_title: Currently with TCC (The Charming Company) as a Project Manager | and | with Ajendo as Head of Sales | Graduated from Maastricht University School of Business and Economics
summary:
My Background:
I was born in the US but I am from Cyprus. 
Fun Fact: I have lived in The Netherlands, Germany, France and Cyprus over the span of last year!  
I am grateful for that experience. I took the opportunity to immerse myself in these cultures and their different ways of working, thinking, living and consuming!

My Interests:
I am intrigued by the minds of consumers and how to find the most effective way to communicate with them; probably why my Sales Conversion Rate is so high.
I am interested in the world of marketing / advertising and design.
And, SEO is my latest fascination.

To sum that up: Consumer behavior and trends pique my curiosity as well as, concepts related to how to appeal to the public eye. 

My Skills:
I consider myself to have highly developed interpersonal, problem-solving, and leadership skills; while also being a great team player who receives feedback well and has amazing attention to detail. 
I am a good communicator and a “people person” (which makes me a great addition to your sales team).
